flick — third-party data attributions

Word-frequency tables (core/assets/freq_en.txt, core/assets/freq_de.txt)
are derived from FrequencyWords by Hermit Dave
(https://github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords — scripts MIT License,
word-frequency content CC-BY-SA-4.0, Copyright (c) 2016 Hermit Dave;
the derived tables here remain under CC-BY-SA-4.0), generated from the
OpenSubtitles 2018 corpus (http://opus.nlpl.eu/OpenSubtitles2018.php).
The tables here are truncated to the 20,000 most frequent words per
language and annotated with quantized Zipf scores.

Public-domain catalog texts (server/assets/catalog/) are sourced from
Project Gutenberg and are in the public domain.
